 have suitable candidates in our network we can start the search, which usually takes a couple of weeks.","_accordion_2_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_3_question":"What type of talent does UMIND have?","_accordion_3_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_3_answer":"At UMIND, we pride ourselves on maintaining a talent pool that is diverse in terms of skill sets, experiences, and backgrounds. Our team of experts includes software developers, UX designers, and project management professionals, among others. Our software developers are highly skilled and experienced in working remotely across various time zones. Prior to joining our team, they undergo a rigorous screening process that evaluates their proficiency in programming languages, as well as their communication skills. When you hire remote software developers at UMIND you get years of experience building top-notch mobile apps, e-commerce stores, SaaS, and web applications for our clients.\\r\\n","_accordion_3_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_4_question":"How does UMIND source candidates?","_accordion_4_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_4_answer":"Approximately half of our candidates are sourced through referrals, highlighting our belief that the most effective approach to attracting exceptional individuals is by seeking recommendations from other exceptional professionals. So you could hire dedicated developers who really will benefit your business. The remaining 50% of our candidate pool is generated through our marketing efforts.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhen it comes to geographical coverage, our primary objective is to facilitate access to a diverse global talent pool for companies. Although we maintain a broader outlook, our current emphasis is on sourcing talent specifically from Eastern and Central Europe.","_accordion_4_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_5_question":"What other services does UMIND provide?","_accordion_5_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_5_answer":"In addition to our talent matching services, we also offer web and application development services similar to that of a development company. Our UMIND project teams consist of a diverse set of cross-functional professionals, including senior project managers, web developers, app developers, and user interface designers, among other technical experts. We have a well-established development process that our team members follow to build fully functional solutions that meet your specific needs.","_accordion_5_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_6_question":"How do I hire a remote developer online?","_accordion_6_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_6_answer":"Leave a request for software developers for hire at our contacts page and get a perfect match within a couple of days. We will be in touch within 24h.","_accordion_6_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion":7,"_accordion":"field_63429a4c9ece3"},"mode":"edit"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/freelancer-block {"name":"acf/freelancer-block","data":{"title":"Are you tired of managing freelancers or hiring software developers?","_title":"field_649033f4a015b","freelancer_0_item":"Skilled tech recruitment and preselected process","_freelancer_0_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_0_image":472,"_freelancer_0_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_1_item":"Unlimited technology stack","_freelancer_1_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_1_image":484,"_freelancer_1_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_2_item":"Work according your company rules and cultural code","_freelancer_2_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_2_image":483,"_freelancer_2_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_3_item":"No administrative burden","_freelancer_3_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_3_image":480,"_freelancer_3_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_4_item":"Cost saving and reasonable rates","_freelancer_4_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_4_image":473,"_freelancer_4_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_5_item":"Savvy En