uff.In case we don’t have suitable candidates in our network we can start the search, which usually takes a couple of weeks.","_accordion_2_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_3_question":"What type of talent does UMIND have?","_accordion_3_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_3_answer":"At UMIND, we pride ourselves on maintaining a talent pool that is diverse in terms of skill sets, experiences, and backgrounds. Our team of experts includes software developers, UX designers, and project management professionals, among others. Our software developers are highly skilled and experienced in working remotely across various time zones. Prior to joining our team, they undergo a rigorous screening process that evaluates their proficiency in programming languages, as well as their communication skills. When you hire remote software developers at UMIND you get years of experience building top-notch mobile apps, e-commerce stores, SaaS, and web applications for our clients.\\r\\n","_accordion_3_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_4_question":"How does UMIND source candidates?","_accordion_4_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_4_answer":"Approximately half of our candidates are sourced through referrals, highlighting our belief that the most effective approach to attracting exceptional individuals is by seeking recommendations from other exceptional professionals. So you could hire dedicated developers who really will benefit your business. The remaining 50% of our candidate pool is generated through our marketing efforts.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhen it comes to geographical coverage, our primary objective is to facilitate access to a diverse global talent pool for companies. Although we maintain a broader outlook, our current emphasis is on sourcing talent specifically from Eastern and Central Europe.","_accordion_4_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_5_question":"What other services does UMIND provide?","_accordion_5_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion