:"field_649325da794c4","hiring3":4,"_hiring3":"field_649325da794c3"},"mode":"edit"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/dev-block {"name":"acf/dev-block","data":{"title":"Enabling businesses to recruit remote developers expands their reach to a vast talent pool unrestricted by geographical boundaries.","_title":"field_64948f97c6e36","sub_title":"UMIND software developers for hire","_sub_title":"field_64948fa3c6e37","dev_inner_left":"Furthermore, this approach proves to be cost-effective, allowing businesses to reduce expenses related to office space, equipment, and recruitment overhead.","_dev_inner_left":"field_6494976b120ba","dev_inner_right":"The inclusion of remote developers from diverse regions and cultures contributes to the infusion of various perspectives and ideas into projects, ultimately fostering a climate of enhanced creativity and innovative problem-solving.","_dev_inner_right":"field_64949781120bb","tab1":"Based on Role","_tab1":"field_6494c5f4b7141","tab2":"On-demand developers","_tab2":"field_6494c604b7142","tab1_inner":"\\u003cspan\\u003eFull stack developers\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eFront-end developers\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eBack-end developers\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eWeb developers\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eMobile developers\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eQA Testers\\u003c/span\\u003e","_tab1_inner":"field_649537af3fb1a","tab2_inner":"If you don’t find the required technology in the list, but you need to hire app developers, \\u003cspan\\u003edrop us a line.\\u003c/span\\u003e We’ll find the matched candidate based on your specific requirements!","_tab2_inner":"field_649537c33fb1b"},"mode":"edit"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/green-block {"name":"acf/green-block","data":{"title":"Tired of tons of CVs and searching for freelancers \\u003cbr\\u003ethat don’t match the \\u003cbr\\u003eproject needs?","_title":"field_64936cb04a999","description":"Contact us  and we will prove a solution.","_description":"field_64943d1fd2356","button":"Hire remote developers","_button":"field_64943d2ad2357","tab1":"Based on Role","_tab1":"field_6494c1ec5c94f","tab2":"On-demand developers","_tab2":"field_6494c1fe5c950","tab1_inner":"","_tab1_inner":"field_6494c232a9658","tab2_inner":"","_tab2_inner":"field_6494c24ea9659"},"mode":"preview"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/accordion-block {"name":"acf/accordion-block","data":{"title":"FAQ","_title":"field_63429a9bb6216","accordion_0_question":"How much does it cost to hire software developers?","_accordion_0_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_0_answer":"Factors like a developer’s experience, development skills \\u0026amp; technology, play an essential role in determining the cost of hiring\\r\\na developer. Share your requirements and we’ll find the perfect match.\\r\\n\\r\\nAt UMIND the rate range is t from 30 to 75 USD per hour. We have\\r\\na developer semi staff cooperation model, where part of the developers are directly hired and the other are contractors, we\\r\\ntake their hourly rate and add our fee on top.","_accordion_0_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_1_question":"What is Free Trial period mentioned in cooperation models?","_accordion_1_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_1_answer":"When  you need app developers for hire you can assign a 1- or 2-day task to the chosen developer to evaluate the real performance and make the final decision before onboarding. No strings attached.\\r\\n","_accordion_1_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_2_question":"How long does it take to hire developers with UMIND?","_accordion_2_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_2_answer":"Having a solid network of remote software developers, the whole process takes from 5 to 10 business days when the request for app developers for hire is left. In most cases we will send you selected CVs within a business day. Then we arrange interviews. If there’s a match, the candidate can start working right away while we sort out the contract stuff.In case we don’t have suitable candidates in our network we can start the search, which usually takes a couple of weeks.","_accordion_2_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_3_question":"What type of talent does UMIND have?","_accordion_3_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_3_answer":"At UMIND, we pride ourselves on maintaining a talent pool that is diverse in terms of skill sets, experiences, and backgrounds. Our team of experts includes software developers, UX designers, and project management professionals, among others. Our software developers are highly skilled and experienced in working remotely across various time zones. Prior to joining our team, they undergo a rigorous screening process that evaluates their proficiency in programming languages, as well as their communication skills. When you hire remote software developers at UMIND you get years of experience building top-notch mobile apps, e-commerce stores, SaaS, and web applications for our clients.\\r\\n","_accordion_3_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_4_question":"How does UMIND source candidates?","_accordion_4_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_4_answer":"Approximately half of our candidates are sourced through referrals, highlighting our belief that the most effective approach to attracting exceptional individuals is by seeking recommendations from other exceptional professionals. So you could hire dedicated developers who really will benefit your business. The remaining 50% of our candidate pool is generated through our marketing efforts.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhen it comes to geographical coverage, our primary objective is to facilitate access to a diverse global talent pool for companies. Although we maintain a broader outlook, our current emphasis is on sourcing talent specifically from Eastern and Central Europe.","_accordion_4_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_5_question":"What other services does UMIND provide?","_accordion_5_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_5_answer":"In addition to our talent matching services, we also offer web and application development services similar to that of a development company. Our UMIND project teams consist of a diverse set of cross-functional professionals, including senior project managers, web developers, app developers, and user interface designers, among other technical experts. We have a well-established development process that our team members follow to build fully functional solutions that meet your specific needs.","_accordion_5_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion_6_question":"How do I hire a remote developer online?","_accordion_6_question":"field_63429a5e9ece4","accordion_6_answer":"Leave a request for software developers for hire at our contacts page and get a perfect match within a couple of days. We will be in touch within 24h.","_accordion_6_answer":"field_63429a699ece5","accordion":7,"_accordion":"field_63429a4c9ece3"},"mode":"edit"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/freelancer-block {"name":"acf/freelancer-block","data":{"title":"Are you tired of managing freelancers or hiring software developers?","_title":"field_649033f4a015b","freelancer_0_item":"Skilled tech recruitment and preselected process","_freelancer_0_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_0_image":472,"_freelancer_0_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_1_item":"Unlimited technology stack","_freelancer_1_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_1_image":484,"_freelancer_1_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_2_item":"Work according your company rules and cultural code","_freelancer_2_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_2_image":483,"_freelancer_2_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_3_item":"No administrative burden","_freelancer_3_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_3_image":480,"_freelancer_3_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_4_item":"Cost saving and reasonable rates","_freelancer_4_item":"field_6490342fa015d","freelancer_4_image":473,"_freelancer_4_image":"field_6490343ea015e","freelancer_5_item":"Savvy 